umc (1.0.4-4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Feature: Add app icon display - fetches and displays actual app icons from Android devices.
  * Feature: Implement fuzzy search algorithm for improved app discovery with relevance scoring.
  * Feature: Add device status indicators - battery level, network type, temperature, and storage information.
  * Feature: Implement device naming/labeling system with persistent custom names.
  * Feature: Add batch app launch - launch apps on multiple devices simultaneously.
  * Feature: Add expandable device cards with detailed status information.
  * Performance: Optimize app list loading - removed blocking operations for faster startup.
  * Performance: Implement lazy icon loading - icons fetch in background without blocking UI.
  * Performance: Reduce icon fetch timeout and make operations cancellable for quick shutdown.
  * Fix: Resolve QML binding loop warnings in main UI.
  * Fix: Add proper null checks for device status properties to prevent QML errors.
  * Fix: Improve cleanup process with timeout-based thread termination.

 -- Unified Mobile Controller Team <umc@project.local>  Sat, 03 Jan 2026 12:00:00 +0000

umc (1.0.4-3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Feature: Add context menu for device actions (Open/Mirror).
  * Feature: Add "New Screen" functionality to open virtual displays (Phone/Tablet/Desktop) without launching an app.
  * Feature: Add "Mirror" functionality to strictly mirror the physical device screen.
  * UI: Add new vector icons for Desktop and Open/Mirror actions.

